snippet.title: SmackDown vs Raw 2011 Nexus DLC Trailer
snippet.description: The Nexus have invaded SmackDown vs Raw 2011, and have brought a few Legendary friends with them for DLC Pack #2. Download it now on XBOX Live Marketplace or the Playstation Store Network.
